# 💻 Example: Factorial

```c id="rq69bh"
#include <stdio.h>

int fact(int n) {
    if(n == 0)
        return 1;

    return n * fact(n - 1);
}

int main() {
    printf("%d", fact(5));
    return 0;
}
```

---

# 🔥 How It Thinks

```id="lkwl5n"
fact(5)
5 * fact(4)
5 * 4 * fact(3)
...
5 * 4 * 3 * 2 * 1
```

👉 Final Answer:

```id="ys43gx"
120
```

