# ⚡ Loop vs Recursion

| Loop                    | Recursion                    |
| ----------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Repeats using condition | Repeats using function calls |
| Uses less memory        | Uses more memory             |
| Faster usually          | Elegant for complex problems |

